Comment: 7 pages, 1 figure. The published version. A figure has been added;
  the list of references has been improved. Some explanatory remarks have been
  included

Comment: 23 pages, 3 figures; this is a revised version, with minor changes in
  definitions and adjustments in the proofs of Lemma 3.3 and Theorem 5.1;
  accepted for publication in Israel Journal of Mathematics

Comment: 123 Pages. Improves The Proof of Theorem 12.1. Keywords: Prime
  Number; Primitive Root; Least Primitive Root; Least Prime Primitive Root;
  Artin Primitive Root Conjecture; Cyclic Group, Algebraic Subsets of Integers

Comment: v1: AMS LaTeX, 20 pages, submitted. v2: AMS LaTeX, 21 pages;
  significant revisions to Sections 4 and 5 following improvements suggested by
  the referee, and references added. To appear in JFA; this is the final
  accepted author manuscript (CC-BY licence). v3: several minor typos fixed;
  metadata and acknowledgements updated
